flowchart TD
  Call[AI tool call] --> Schema[Validate input schema]
  Schema --> Safe[Check path and tool policy]
  Safe --> Type{Tool type}
  Type -->|Read / analysis| Read[Read file, list, search, analyze]
  Read --> Executed[Log executed code_analysis]
  Type -->|File mutation| StageFile[Update overlay or deleted set]
  StageFile --> PendingFile[Log pending file action]
  Type -->|Folder creation| StageFolder[Log pending folder action]
  Type -->|Shell| StageShell[Log pending shell command]
  PendingFile --> Approval[Approval workflow]
  StageFolder --> Approval
  StageShell --> Approval
  Approval -->|Approved| Apply[Apply approved actions]
  Approval -->|Rejected| Clear[Clear staging]
  Apply --> Clear
